<%- include('partials/header') %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<main id="main-content">
    <section class="section" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-50), var(--beige));">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-badge">What We Offer</span>
                <h2>Our Tutoring Services</h2>
                <p>Everything your child needs to thrive academically, all in one place.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="card service-card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--blue-500);">
                    <div class="card-icon blue" aria-hidden="true" style="width:72px;height:72px;font-size:2rem;">&#x1F393;</div>
                    <h3>One-on-One Tutoring</h3>
                    <p>Your child gets undivided attention from an expert tutor. Every lesson is tailored to their pace, learning style, and goals. This is where real breakthroughs happen.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card service-card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--yellow-400);">
                    <div class="card-icon yellow" aria-hidden="true" style="width:72px;height:72px;font-size:2rem;">&#x1F46B;</div>
                    <h3>Small Group Sessions</h3>
                    <p>2 to 4 students learn together with a dedicated tutor. Peer interaction, friendly competition, and collaborative problem-solving make learning social and fun.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card service-card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--blue-400);">
                    <div class="card-icon blue" aria-hidden="true" style="width:72px;height:72px;font-size:2rem;">&#x1F4BB;</div>
                    <h3>Live Video Sessions</h3>
                    <p>Learn from anywhere with our built-in video calls. No apps to download, no accounts to create. Just click "Join" from your dashboard and start learning.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card service-card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--orange-500);">
                    <div class="card-icon orange" aria-hidden="true" style="width:72px;height:72px;font-size:2rem;">&#x1F4CA;</div>
                    <h3>Monthly Progress Reports</h3>
                    <p>Every month, tutors send detailed report cards with grades, performance scores, strengths, areas to improve, and goals. Parents always know where their child stands.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card service-card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--yellow-500);">
                    <div class="card-icon yellow" aria-hidden="true" style="width:72px;height:72px;font-size:2rem;">&#x1F4D6;</div>
                    <h3>27+ Subjects</h3>
                    <p>Math, Science, English, History, Languages, Test Prep, Computer Science, and more. From elementary through college level, we cover it all.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card service-card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--blue-600);">
                    <div class="card-icon blue" aria-hidden="true" style="width:72px;height:72px;font-size:2rem;">&#x1F4AC;</div>
                    <h3>Direct Parent Access</h3>
                    <p>Message your child's tutor anytime. Submit feedback, ask questions, or file concerns through your dashboard. You are always part of the learning process.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="background:var(--white);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-badge">How It Works</span>
                <h2>Three Steps to Better Grades</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="steps-grid">
                <div style="text-align:center;">
                    <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue-500),var(--blue-700));color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;margin:0 auto 16px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(37,99,235,0.3);">1</div>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">Book a Free Call</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);">Tell us about your child. We will understand their challenges, goals, and learning style in a quick 15-minute call.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align:center;">
                    <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--yellow-400),var(--yellow-500));color:var(--gray-900);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;margin:0 auto 16px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(245,158,11,0.3);">2</div>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">Get Matched</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);">We hand-pick a tutor who specializes in your child's subject and connects with their personality. Not a random assignment.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align:center;">
                    <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue-400),var(--blue-600));color:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;margin:0 auto 16px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(96,165,250,0.3);">3</div>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:8px;">Watch Them Grow</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);">Sessions begin! Track progress on your dashboard, read monthly reports, and see your child's confidence build week by week.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:48px;">
                <a href="/consultation" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Your Free Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;text-align:center;">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom:16px;">What Makes Our Sessions Different</h2>
            <p style="color:var(--gray-500);font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:32px;">Every session is recorded in a session sheet by the tutor, covering what was taught, homework assigned, student performance, and plans for next time. Parents can see everything. No guessing, no surprises.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:20px;">
                <div class="card" style="padding:24px;text-align:center;">
                    <p style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:8px;">&#x1F3AF;</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1rem;">Tailored Lessons</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);font-size:0.9rem;">No cookie-cutter curriculum</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card" style="padding:24px;text-align:center;">
                    <p style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:8px;">&#x1F4C5;</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1rem;">Flexible Scheduling</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);font-size:0.9rem;">Book times that work for you</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card" style="padding:24px;text-align:center;">
                    <p style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:8px;">&#x1F4DD;</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1rem;">Session Reports</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);font-size:0.9rem;">After every single session</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card" style="padding:24px;text-align:center;">
                    <p style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:8px;">&#x1F4B0;</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size:1rem;">Gives Back</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--gray-500);font-size:0.9rem;">Part of proceeds to charity</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
